summary: An ordinance relating to the condemnation proceedings for the acquisition of sewer easements in Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M in Block 4, Plat of Allendale, and in Tract 34, Bitter Lake Villa Tracts, under Ordinance 88403, King County Cause No. 542188, making an appropriation from the Sewer Fund for payment of costs and awards when accepted.
